 ↞---------------|ABILITIES|---------------↠

  Suction-cups:

    This Pokémon cannot be forced 
  out of battle by moves such as 
  whirlwind.

  dragon tail and circle throw 
  still inflict damage against 
  this Pokémon.

  Overworld: If the lead Pokémon 
  has this ability, the success 
  rate while fishing is increased.

  Sniper:

    This Pokémon inflicts triple 
  damage with critical hits, rather 
  than the usual double damage.

  Moody:

    After each turn, one of this 
  Pokémon's stats at random rises 
  two stages, and another falls 
  one stage.

  If a stat is already at 6 or 
  -6 stages, it will not be chosen 
  to be increased or decreased, 
  respectively.


